                            <div id="description" itemprop="description">
                                <p>Kaizen is the ultimate theme for a blog. It has a front page that gives you lots of display options all in a simple and elegant design that makes your content take front stage.</p>
<p>Kaizen theme also ensures your blog posts look great with a range of text styles for your posts.</p>
<p><strong>Features</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Clean Header and Footer</li>
<li>Bread crumb navigation in posts and pages</li>
<li>Featured Posts</li>
<li>Two Column Template </li>
<li>Right Sidebar</li>
<li>Template for Tag Cloud</li>
<li>Beautiful Comment System</li>
<li>Search Box Ready</li>
<li>Social Media Icons </li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Code</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Uses Bootstrap 2.0.3</li>
<li>Written in valid html5 syntax and semantics</li>
<li>Styles for tags and comments</li>
<li>Includes jquery 1.7.1</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Fonts</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Open Sans</li>
<li>Helvetica Neue</li>
<li>Google Fonts</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Assests</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Header image</li>
<li>Footer images</li>
<li>Social Icons</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Contact</strong></p>
<p>If you have any queries related to this theme, contact me...</p>
<p>Remember, this theme is built with twitter bootstrap so you have access to entire library of html, css components.</p>
